# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:23
msgid "Learn More"
msgstr "تعرف على المزيد"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:24
msgid ""
"We are working hard to expand this user guide and to improve OpenShot Video "
"Editor, but if you are stuck and don't know where to turn, OpenShot has "
"several sources for additional information."
msgstr ""
"نحن نعمل جاهدين على توسيع دليل المستخدم هذا وتحسين OpenShot Video Editor، "
"ولكن إذا كنت عالقًا ولا تعرف إلى أين تتجه، لدى OpenShot عدة مصادر لمزيد من "
"المعلومات."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:27
msgid ""
"OpenShot has several `YouTube Tutorials <https://www.youtube.com/playlist?"
"list=PLymupH2aoNQNezYzv2lhSwvoyZgLp1Q0T>`_ available to help you learn more."
msgstr ""
"يوجد لدى OpenShot عدة `دروس على YouTube <https://www.youtube.com/playlist?"
"list=PLymupH2aoNQNezYzv2lhSwvoyZgLp1Q0T>`_ لمساعدتك على التعلم أكثر."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:28
msgid ""
"OpenShot has a `Reddit User Community <https://openshot.org/forum>`_ "
"dedicated to users helping users, answering questions, and discussing video "
"editing and OpenShot topics."
msgstr ""
"لدى OpenShot `مجتمع مستخدمي Reddit <https://openshot.org/forum>`_ مخصص "
"لمساعدة المستخدمين بعضهم البعض، والإجابة على الأسئلة، ومناقشة تحرير الفيديو "
"ومواضيع OpenShot."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:29
msgid ""
"If you would like to help improve this User Guide, `view source on GitHub "
"<https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/tree/develop/doc>`_."
msgstr ""
"إذا كنت ترغب في المساعدة في تحسين دليل المستخدم هذا، `عرض المصدر على GitHub "
"<https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/tree/develop/doc>`_."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:30
msgid ""
"If you have discovered a new bug, please `Report a Bug <https://www.openshot."
"org/issues/new/>`_."
msgstr ""
"إذا اكتشفت خطأً جديدًا، يرجى `الإبلاغ عن خطأ <https://www.openshot.org/issues/"
"new/>`_."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:31
msgid ""
"If you need professional support, you can open a ticket by sending an "
"message to support@openshot.org or `Schedule a call <https://calendly.com/"
"openshot-support/desktop>`_."
msgstr ""
"إذا كنت بحاجة إلى دعم احترافي، يمكنك فتح تذكرة بإرسال رسالة إلى "
"support@openshot.org أو `جدولة مكالمة <https://calendly.com/openshot-support/"
"desktop>`_."
